                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18420509-1619-offence-1 t18420509-cd-171"></join>12th of May</rs>, 1 handkerchief, value 4<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18420509-name-1028" type="victimName">
